A woman with elegant brown hair, half pinned with jeweled accessories, wearing an emerald chiffon dress, approached with the sound of clicking heels. Realizing the two knew each other, Victor quietly stepped back.

 

“Ulrich.”

 

Her voice was as graceful as a wild rose.

 

